{"tid":1565163,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"噚晚十一點半旺角站衝閘嗰兩個男仔同我入嚟","createTime":"2019-09-13T04:53:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T04:55:26.000Z","uid":159172,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d66bb2d223fe7480de1bd4630593a2a3486635e6","tid":1565163,"uid":159172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:53:35.000Z","msg":"是咁的尋晚送完女神旺角搭車返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。 佢住得遠無辦法都要搭黨鐵。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n見到有兩個好似中學生咁嘅年紀嘅男仔諗住試下衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，又好似唔夠膽衝咁樣。 我好怕俾到壓力你，所以即刻擰轉面用部電話反射咁gup。<br />\n<br />\n睇到你哋想試下跨過個閘，又唔夠高令警報響咗，忍唔住又縮返返去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同行個女仔叫你哋都係算啦然後行咗去客服。見到你哋真係垂頭喪氣噉樣行咗客服嗰陣，係有少少灰鳩，想行過去鼓勵下你哋。<br />\n<br />\n行到去嘅時候，你哋又咁啱搞掂啲唔知乜嘢，一行人行返去部機。 條女頭也不會咁樣拍卡入咗閘。<br />\n<br />\n然後你哋兩個猶疑咗十秒....<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">然之後一齊爬咗欄桿同閘機中間嗰個位/一嘢跳咗入去。</span></span></em></strong><br />\n條女聽唔到八達通聲但係見到佢哋兩個係後面呆撚咗，我忍唔住差啲拍手掌。<br />\n<br />\n屌你見到真係忍唔住做咗劉馬車個細佬，流馬尿好撚感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。 即刻沖咗去同佢講聲巴打好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仔呀，見你哋個樣都應該係平時好撚乖， 人哋娘親都唔會問候。 跳閘呢啲嘢一次生兩次熟，你衝破咗個心理關口就做到㗎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢個年紀係應該溝下女同friend出去玩下， 呢幾日趁無咩事中秋節玩得開心啲知唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7522fc93a2d60ca2bad80ddd018da3fe85f356b0","tid":1565163,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:54:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"038a2bbb1160dcd2ccaec8384c3168ad5249125a","tid":1565163,"uid":30201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:55:26.000Z","msg":"中秋自選活動 祝大家平平安安 團團圓圓<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wink.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n►人鏈活動◄<br />\n1630 石硤尾聯校人鏈&gt;集合點: 黃棣珊中學正門<br />\n1930 屯門牛牛人鏈&gt;集合點: 顯發里對出空地<br />\n2100 將軍澳人鏈&gt;調景嶺站&rarr;單車公園&larr;寶康公園<br />\n2130 沙田城門河人鏈 (直接去最接近你既河邊集合)<br />\n-------------------------------------<br />\n►快閃大合唱◄<br />\n1300 中環&gt;遮打花園<br />\n1300 太古&gt;OIE樓下水池<br />\n1930 屯門&gt;顯發里對出空地<br />\n-------------------------------------<br />\n►獅子山之路，齊慶中秋夜◄<br />\n1900 大圍、樂富、黃大仙等入口集合<br />\n-------------------------------------<br />\n►18區賞燈晚會 ◄ (如無注明則2030開始)<br />\n【新界西】<br />\n屯門顯發里對出空地 (承接大合唱)<br />\n屯門公園<br />\n天水圍公園<br />\n元朗公園<br />\n荃灣公園海濱長廊<br />\n葵涌運動場籃球場，林士德遊樂場<br />\n青衣海濱長廊<br />\n【新界東】<br />\n1900 上水陳融中學旁紅場<br />\n沙田中央公園<br />\n大埔海濱公園 ，大埔中央公園<br />\n馬鞍山公園<br />\n將軍澳海濱公園，寶康公園<br />\n【九龍】<br />\n美孚嶺南之風<br />\n長沙灣遊樂場<br />\n深水埗通州街遊樂場<br />\n尖沙咀梳